Covert Skins.name: AUG | Chameleon
Covert Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with the image of a chameleon.
Covert Skins.lore: Subtlety can make all the difference

Covert Skins.name: AWP | Asiimov
Covert Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a sci-fi design.
Covert Skins.lore: Anyone can predict the future... a visionary shapes it

Classified Skins.name: Nova | Antique
Classified Skins.desc: It has been painted using a combination of hydrographics and dry-transfer decals to create the look of a wood stock and gold inlay.
Classified Skins.lore: With age comes wisdom and stopping power

Classified Skins.name: P90 | Trigon
Classified Skins.desc: It has been custom painted in contrasting orange, grey and black.

Classified Skins.name: AK-47 | Redline
Classified Skins.desc: It has been painted using a carbon fiber hydrographic and a dry-transfer decal of a red pinstripe.
Classified Skins.lore: Never be afraid to push it to the limit

Restricted Skins.name: USP-S | Guardian
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been painted cobalt blue and stenciled with the CT logo on the slide.
Restricted Skins.lore: I can follow procedure and get 7 out, or I can do it my way and save all 10... your choice - Carmen Cocinero, Extraction Expert

Restricted Skins.name: FAMAS | Sergeant
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been given a patina of varying depth using masking fluid to create a military motif, sealed with a satin finish.

Restricted Skins.name: SG 553 | Pulse
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been painted with a hydrographic of bold fuchsia fragments.
Restricted Skins.lore: Striking colors for a striking weapon

Restricted Skins.name: MAC-10 | Heat
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted to look as though it just came out of the forge.
Restricted Skins.lore: Make some outlines of your own

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Negev | Terrain
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been painted using a hydrographic with a terrain motif.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: For someone who is supposed to be impartial, your daughter made an interesting choice for companionship - The Father and The Phoenix Part 1

Mil-Spec Skins.name: MAG-7 | Heaven Guard
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been painted using a combination of subtly patterned hydrographics and dry-transfer decals of wings.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Sometimes the wings of an angel don't mean salvation

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Tec-9 | Sandstorm
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been painted using a hydrographic in a purple and beige graphic design.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: It'll take more than a tarp to protect you

Mil-Spec Skins.name: UMP-45 | Corporal
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted in a military motif.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Respect can never be taken, only earned
